::Dark One::

Dark One swoops into the base, still in jet fighter mode. He flies down a 
ways down a hallway before landing.

"Blast panels," he says as his cockpit opens. Blast panels drop on either 
side of the hallway, closing Dark One and Squizzy in.

"You may get out," he says, "Do you need a CR chamber?"
